Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.60,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.77,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:39.94,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:40.82,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.69,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,There's a strange old man outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.48,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.78,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,No... That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.28,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.28,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi, he's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.57,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:49.70,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Both of you, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.66,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,That's our neighbor, Matsui-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:55.75,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call him a "strange old man"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.92,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:06.43,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sor...ry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:08.80,Main Dialog,Matsui-san,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.81,Main Dialog,Matsui-san,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, my sudden \Ngreeting frightened him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:13.56,Main Dialog,Matsui-san,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.56,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, he was incredibly rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.19,Main Dialog,Matsui-san,0000,0000,0000,,Well, be careful going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.69,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:27.86,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.91,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,When you ran away, you \Ndragged Rin along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:36.33,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,But Kouki-kun made a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.42,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,If Kouki's with you, I feel \Na little more reassured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:41.00,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.13,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:43.25,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:44.92,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.51,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be late...
